{"tid":1623534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[和理非] 全部和理非同我入黎","createTime":"2019-10-04T23:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T23:55:53.000Z","uid":2787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"0c29af037b480499fdffa935ca4fb5a453506f59","tid":1623534,"uid":2787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:35:46.000Z","msg":"對於外界質疑實施《禁止蒙面規例》會在流感高峰期間影響預防流感措施，對公共衞生造成影響。政府發言人強調，<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>新規例跟公共衞生的呼籲是沒有抵觸，有關規例不會禁止市民因其健康需要佩戴口罩，以預防疾病感染或傳播。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n佩戴口罩是預防呼吸道感染的其中一個方法，為防止傳染病例如流感的傳播，政府建議一系列的防禦措施，包括接種相關疫苗，保持良好個人和環境衞生。<br />\n<br />\n#香港電台 #禁蒙面法 #口罩 #流感<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔好個個驚左反口罩就唔上街唔戴口罩<br />\nSource : 香港電台視像新聞 RTHK VNEWS Facebook<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37ca745c11f80bd53876d5059e56bf4a41f63ac8","tid":1623534,"uid":2787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:36:19.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"f17cce58b3ac0d83d9ab924fa6b078d703bd0b8e","tid":1623534,"uid":2787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:36:31.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"a10a82cc5ec17de2c06fea31a0aca421f281a1ff","tid":1623534,"uid":2787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:36:44.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"2d93d527c682ccb765b2221c4c104089af2cd303","tid":1623534,"uid":2787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:37:00.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"b6b5915b090c3e4bd8b172c6d2bea09762443d83","tid":1623534,"uid":2787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:37:15.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"245942cd5ab80b98f5070c1a5aa1f81f490bb00a","tid":1623534,"uid":2787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T23:37:41.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"aa04a41ca56c4967ec27